strings: <voice_0x01000B1E><se_low>King of tricks: I understand, I understand! It finally works!
<voice_0x01000B1F><se_low>King of tricks: <hero> thanks halfway! I have to show you something!
<voice_0x01000B20><se_low>King of tricks: this is it! It's just like a normal pot, right? However, it was actually a legendary alchemical cauldron!
<voice_0x01000B21><se_low>King of tricks: ... I see that you do not mind. let me explain
<voice_0x01000B22><se_low>King of tricks: The Cauldron Alchemist was an invaluable tool for creating all kinds of things.
<voice_0x01000B23><se_low>King of tricks: Combine different materials to craft rare items, armor and weapons.
<voice_0x01000B24><se_low>King of tricks: He cursed my kingdom, thinking that it would work and that I would get him out of the palace.
<voice_0x01000B25><se_low>King of tricks: Last but not least, do a 24 hour reset. No, I will thank you later.
<voice_0x01000B26><se_low>King of tricks: Well, it's fashionable, so why not try it? user-friendly
You can now use the Trodecking Alchemy Deck in your party!
<voice_0x01000B28><se_def>Copper Head: Ready to pack and go!
<voice_0x01000B2A><se_def>that needs maintenance: He's coming! Take me to the Port of Elurod.
